content:
aadyaachaaryathvam kykko-
baharon mooshayotonnicchu
skariyaaykkathu nalki mooshaa
sariyaa yohannaaneki;
/tyohannaan kartthaavinnum;
/tkartthaa than shleehanmaarkkum;
naanaasrushtivibhaagangalkkeki shleehanmaar.

aachaaryathvam mun nirtthi shlee-haril mumpan
sheemonotu naathan chonnori-naadam hrudyam;
“ninne gruhanaayakanaakki-tthanneetunnen
ambaradharani'bandhanamukthitthaa-kkolukal; 'nee
/tbandhicchaal-njaanum bandhikkum;
/tmochicchaal-mochikkum njaanum;
paapikale prathi abhyarththicchennaal-ketteetum'.

sleebaa vennu; vellunnu;
sleebaa vidveshiye vennu;
sleebaaye saakshicchorkkaayu
sleebaayaakatte kotta.
